    <string name="fasting_desc_16_8">Leangains – fast for 16 h, eat within 8 h. The most popular and best-studied protocol; usually you skip breakfast. A great entry point.</string>
    <string name="fasting_desc_18_6">Fast for 18 h, eat within 6 h. A bit stricter than 16:8, may boost fat loss and autophagy. For intermediate practitioners.</string>
    <string name="fasting_desc_14_10">Fast for 14 h, eat within 10 h. A gentle, everyday-friendly entry point for beginners.</string>
    <string name="fasting_desc_20_4">Warrior Diet – fast for 20 h, eat within 4 h (one main meal). Advanced; make sure to get enough protein and micronutrients.</string>
    <string name="fasting_desc_omad">One Meal A Day – fast for about 23 h, one meal per day. Very advanced; meeting nutrient needs in a single meal is challenging.</string>
    <string name="fasting_desc_5_2">Eat normally on 5 days, reduce to ~500–600 kcal on 2 non-consecutive days. Day-based – no hourly countdown.</string>
